Aerofly FS 2 Flight Simulator lets you explore the world of flying in a
  quality never seen before. Fly a large selection of highly detailed
  aircraft with interactive 3D cockpits. Aerofly FS 2 currently features over
  150 airports in the south western USA and global elevation and satellite
  imagery.
  
  This pack includes the following DLC's:
  
  * Aerofly FS 2 - Orbx - Chicago Meigs Field
  * Aerofly FS 2 - Orbx - Innsbruck Airport
  * Aerofly FS 2 - Northeastern USA
  * Aerofly FS 2 - Switzerland
